<plot>Asfour wants to marry his boss' daughter Aleya, but Aleya's father rejects him because of his lower class and his lack of money. Asfour later meets a mysterious old man who advises him to go to a cave in the mountain, where he will find bliss. The cave contains a magical lamp with a female genie named Kahramana. Asfour commands her to assist him in his desire to win Aleya, but the genie has plans of her own for him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?024923</url></doc>
